# textdomain: mcl_tnt
An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings and destroy blocks around it. TNT has an explosion power of @1. With a small chance, blocks may drop as an item (as if being mined) rather than being destroyed. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals.=Lehergailu bat. Lehertzen denean, inguruko blokeak puskatu eta izakiei min emango die. Dinamitak @1 eztanda-potentzia du. Probabilitate txiki batekin, blokeak item eran eror daitezke (ustiatzean bezala) suntsitu beharrean. Tresnekin, leherketekin, suarekin, labarekin eta redstone seinaleekin piztu daiteke dinamita.
An explosive device. When it explodes, it will hurt living beings. TNT has an explosion power of @1. TNT can be ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava and redstone signals.=Lehergailu bat. Lehertzen denean, izaki bizidunei mina emango die. Dinamitak @1 eztanda-potentzia du. Tresnekin, leherketekin, suarekin, labarekin eta redstone seinaleekin piztu daiteke dinamita.
TNT=Dinamita
Ignited by tools, explosions, fire, lava, redstone power=Tresnekin, leherketekin, suarekin, labarekin eta redstone seinaleekin piztua
Explosion power: @1=Leherketa-ahalmena: @1
Place the TNT and ignite it with one of the methods above. Quickly get in safe distance. The TNT will start to be affected by gravity and explodes in 4 seconds.=Jarri dinamita eta piztu aurreko metodoetako batekin. Urrundu azkar distantzia seguru batera. Dinamitari grabitateak eragingo dio eta 4 segundotan lehertuko da.
